trans-unit.source: Enables queuing support for the marked assembly and enables the application to read method calls from Message Queuing queues.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer queuing støtte for merkede samlingen, og gjør at appen kan lese metodekall fra Message Queueing-køer.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: For a list of initial property values for an instance of ApplicationQueuingAttribute, see the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: En liste med opprinnelige verdier for en forekomst av ApplicationQueuingAttribute, kan du se den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about using attributes, see [Attributes](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om hvordan du bruker attributter [attributter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute"></xref> class, enabling queuing support for the assembly and initializing <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute.Enabled*>, <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute.QueueListenerEnabled*>, and <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute.MaxListenerThreads*>.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute"> </xref> klassen aktivering queuing støtte for samlingen og initialiserer <> </> *>, <> </> *>, og <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute.MaxListenerThreads*>.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute.MaxListenerThreads*>

trans-unit.source: The following table shows initial property values for an instance of <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute>.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser første egenskapsverdier for en forekomst av <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute>.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute>

trans-unit.source: |Property|Value| |--------------|-----------| |`Enabled`|`true`| |`QueueListenerEnabled`|`false`| |`MaxListenerThreads`|zero (0)|
trans-unit.target: | Egenskapen | Verdien | |--------------|-----------| | `Enabled`|`true`| | `QueueListenerEnabled`|`false`| | `MaxListenerThreads`|zero (0)|

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether queuing support is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om queuing støtte er aktivert.

trans-unit.source: Applications are not able to use queued components by default.
trans-unit.target: Programmer kan ikke bruke komponenter som standard.

trans-unit.source: Instantiating <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute> enables an application to use queued components; however, it does not enable the application to listen for queued messages from clients.
trans-unit.target: Start av <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute>aktiverer en applikasjon å bruke komponenter i kø; imidlertid den ikke aktiverer programmet til å lytte etter meldingene i køen fra klienter.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.ApplicationQueuingAttribute>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if queuing support is enabled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis queuing støtte er aktivert. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default value set by the constructor is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien som er angitt av konstruktøren <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the number of threads used to extract messages from the queue and activate the corresponding component.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir antall tråder som brukes til å hente meldinger fra køen og aktivere den tilsvarende komponenten.

trans-unit.source: The valid range for this property is 0 to 1000.
trans-unit.target: Det gyldige området for denne egenskapen er 0 til 1000.

trans-unit.source: The default is zero.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er null.

trans-unit.source: For a newly created application, the setting is derived from the algorithm currently used for determining the default number of listener threads: 16 times the number of CPUs in the server.
trans-unit.target: For en nyopprettede applikasjon innstillingen er avledet av algoritmen som brukes til å bestemme standardantall tråder som lytter: 16 ganger antall CPUer på serveren.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see `QcListenerMaxThreads` in [Applications (COM+)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/cossdk/html/c0c46592-5282-412d-8f54-67637be8218a.asp).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se `QcListenerMaxThreads` i [programmer (COM +)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/cossdk/html/c0c46592-5282-412d-8f54-67637be8218a.asp).

trans-unit.source: The maximum number of threads to use for processing messages arriving in the queue.
trans-unit.target: Maksimalt antall tråder som skal brukes for behandling av meldinger som ankommer i køen.

trans-unit.source: The default is zero.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er null.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the application will accept queued component calls from clients.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om programmet godtar i kø komponent kall fra klienter.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the application accepts queued component calls; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis programmet godtar samtaler i kø komponent; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
